info.description:
Hi,

This program is a web application which enables users to build a Fedora
Spin/Remix. It is a Free Software liscenced under the GNU Affero General 
Public License and written using Django/Python.

The project is hosted at https://fedorahosted.org/dorrie/ and its wiki is
located at https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Remixes_Web_Interface

For installation related information see INSTALL
info.keywords: fedora kickstart python dorrie django redhat rit
